# Only the scraper script + its single import are needed in the image.
# Everything else from the hub repo (Next.js app, dashboard, tests,
# build artifacts) just bloats the build context and slows pushes.
*
!scraper/Dockerfile
!scraper/package.json
!scraper/package-lock.json
!lib/priceExtractor.ts
!scripts/scrape-landing-prices.mjs
